ulder/}}</ref>。嫌犯艾哈迈德·阿里维·艾萨被控10项一级谋杀罪<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/man-charged-10-counts-first-degree-murder-after-shooting-colorado-n1261808|title=Man charged with 10 counts of first-degree murder in Colorado grocery store shooting|website=NBC News|last=Li|first=David K.|date=2021-03-23|access-date=2021-03-23|archive-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523173728/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/man-charged-10-counts-first-degree-murder-after-shooting-colorado-n1261808|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该案是3月16日[[2021年亚特兰大按摩中心枪击案|亚特兰大按摩中心枪击案]]相隔不到一个星期后美国又一起枪击案。

== 過程 ==
[[北美山区时区|北美山区时区]]3月22日下午2点半后，枪手手持一把{{link-en|AR-15突击步枪|AR-15 style rifle}}进入[[金苏柏|金苏柏]]超市掃射<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=At least 10 dead after shooting inside a King Soopers in Boulder|url=https://nypost.com/2021/03/22/police-at-scene-of-active-shooter-at-colorado-supermarket/|accessdate=2021-03-22|author=Fitz-Gibbon|date=2021-03-22|first=Jorge|work=New York Post|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523173719/https://nypost.com/2021/03/22/police-at-scene-of-active-shooter-at-colorado-supermarket/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

槍擊案發生後，博尔德警察局接到報警稱有人携带步枪。博尔德警官埃里克·塔利（Eric Talley）隨後趕到槍擊現場，不過他被兇手开枪打死<ref>{{Cite web|title=Slain Boulder police officer Eric Talley was first to respond at the scene, says police chief|url=https://www.cnn.com/us/live-news/colorado-king-soopers-shooting/h_183ea3c64ed7ad8df3ff947faa66275a|accessdate=2021-03-22|author=Ryan|date=2021-03-22|first=Josiah|archive-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523173735/https://www.cnn.com/us/live-news/colorado-king-soopers-shooting/h_183ea3c64ed7ad8df3ff947faa66275a|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在警方抵达现场约2小时后，一名受傷男子被逮捕<ref>{{cite news|title=美国科罗拉多州一超市发生枪击案 造成10人死亡|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/03-23/9438430.shtml|work=中国新闻网|date=2021-03-23|language=zh|accessdate=2021-03-23|archive-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523173724/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/03-23/9438430.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 兇手 ==
嫌犯艾哈迈德·阿利维·阿里萨（Ahmad Al Aliwi Alissa）是一名出生於1999年的[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]男子，已入籍美國<ref>{{Cite web|title=Lawyer: Colorado shooting suspect needs mental health review|url=https://apnews.com/article/ahmad-al-aliwi-alissa-1st-court-appearance-boulder-shooting-d870b03a763d8b20fdfa04a26a1379a1|access-date=2021-06-01|author=COLLEEN SLEVIN, BERNARD CONDON, THOMAS PEIPERT, PATTY NIEBERG|date=2021-04-20|work=AP NEWS|publisher=[[美联社|美联社]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517131137/https://apnews.com/article/ahmad-al-aliwi-alissa-1st-court-appearance-boulder-shooting-d870b03a763d8b20fdfa04a26a1379a1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite news|title=Colorado suspect's family saw him fiddling with gun days before shooting -court documents|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-colorado-shooting-suspect-idUSKBN2BF2WW|newspaper=Reuters|date=2021-03-24|accessdate=2021-06-01|language=en|first=Nathan|last=Layne|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420015716/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-colorado-shooting-suspect-idUSKBN2BF2WW|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同家人于2002年移民美国，于2014年移居到[[阿瓦达_(科罗拉多州)|阿瓦达]]<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Here's what we know about the Boulder, Colorado, mass shooting suspect|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/03/23/us/boulder-colorado-shooting-suspect/index.html|access-date=2021-06-01|last=CNN|first=Ray Sanchez, Paul Murphy, Blake Ellis and Amir Vera|work=CNN|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606150601/https://www.cnn.com/2021/03/23/us/boulder-colorado-shooting-suspect/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其大部分時間居住在美國，畢業於[[阿瓦达西高中|阿瓦达西高中]]。其同學透露，阿里萨脾气暴躁。2017年11月，阿里萨在學校裡將另一名學生打暈，並於2018年被判[[三級襲擊|三級襲擊]]<ref name=":1" /><ref name="紐約時報" />，阿里萨表示，該同学曾用[[种族用语|种族用语]]称呼他。2018年，阿里萨因涉嫌破坏罪被捕<ref name="紐約時報">{{cite news|title=科罗拉多枪击案幸存者：“听着他杀死所有你认识的人”|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20210324/boulder-shooting/|author=JACK HEALY, NICHOLAS BOGEL-BURROUGHS|work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|date=2021-03-24|language=zh|accessdate=2021-03-24|archive-date=2021-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210604132445/https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20210324/boulder-shooting/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

兇手的哥哥阿里·阿利维·阿里萨（Ali Aliwi Alissa）表示，阿里萨从2014年左右开始越来越偏执、反社会，认为自己被人跟踪和追捕<ref name=":1" /><ref name="紐約時報" />，另外阿里萨的哥哥认为学校里的欺凌和言语可能导致了阿里萨的偏执<ref>{{Cite web|title=Suspected Boulder shooter was bullied, anti-social and paranoid, brother says|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/boulder-shooter-name-colorado-gunman-b1821207.html|access-date=2021-06-01|date=2021-03-23|work=The Independent|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421232022/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/boulder-shooter-name-colorado-gunman-b1821207.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2" />。阿里萨曾经擔心被人監視，用胶带將电脑的摄像头遮住<ref name=紐約時報/>。

